CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Arrive AI (NASDAQ: ARAI) is building the autonomous delivery network of the future-anchored by AI-powered Arrive Points TM that secure, track, and protect every package down to the final inch. Our platform is built on foundational IP and our proprietary hardware and software, enabling asynchronous delivery between people, robots, and drones. From pharmaceuticals to e-commerce, ARAI delivers chain-of-custody assurance with smart infrastructure that scales.
